                                    </div>
                                    <div class="common-comment__blog-2">
                                        <div class="Comment_blog-tittle-body">
                                            <div class="CommentBox_commentWrapper">
                                                <img src="/img/anh.png" alt="" class="postItem__author-img news-blog__postItem__author-img news-blog__postItem__author-img-comment">
